public class QWindowsStyle
extends QCommonStyle

The QWindowsStyle class provides a Microsoft Windows-like look and feel. This style is Qt's default GUI style on Windows.


See also:
QWindowsXPStyle, QMacStyle, QPlastiqueStyle, QCDEStyle, and QMotifStyle.
